translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: (Well, since there's contraceptive magic, no child will be born though.)

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「もし、次に産むことがあったら、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "If I were to give birth next time,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 次は女の子にしろ、女の子に」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: next time it has to be a girl, a girl."
